---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="首页 | 我的个人网站" description="欢迎访问我的个人网站，了解我的项目和博客">
  <section class="hero min-h-96 bg-base-200">
    <div class="hero-content flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse">
      <img src="/images/profile.jpg" class="max-w-sm rounded-lg shadow-2xl" alt="个人照片" />
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">您好，我是XXX</h1>
        <p class="py-6">我是一名热爱技术的开发者，专注于Web开发和用户体验设计。欢迎来到我的个人网站，这里展示了我的项目、博客以及一些个人信息。</p>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">了解更多</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">我的技能</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">前端开发</h3>
            <p>精通HTML、CSS、JavaScript，熟悉现代前端框架如React、Vue和Astro，以及TailwindCSS等UI库。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">后端开发</h3>
            <p>熟悉Node.js、Python等后端技术，有丰富的API开发和数据库设计经验。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">UI/UX设计</h3>
            <p>具有良好的审美能力和用户体验设计理念，能够设计直观且美观的用户界面。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-base-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">最新项目</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <figure><img src="/images/project1.jpg" alt="项目1" /></figure>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">汉服文化网站</h3>
            <p>一个展示汉服文化的静态网站，使用HTML、CSS和JavaScript构建。</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-primary">查看详情</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <figure><img src="/images/project2.jpg" alt="项目2" /></figure>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">个人博客系统</h3>
            <p>基于Astro和TailwindCSS构建的个人博客系统，支持Markdown内容。</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-primary">查看详情</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">最新博客文章</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">Astro框架初体验</h3>
            <p>分享我使用Astro框架构建网站的经验和心得。</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">阅读全文</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">TailwindCSS使用技巧</h3>
            <p>介绍一些TailwindCSS的实用技巧和最佳实践。</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">阅读全文</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">静态网站生成器对比</h3>
            <p>对比几种流行的静态网站生成器，帮助你选择适合的工具。</p>
            <div class="card-actions justify-end">
              <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">阅读全文</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-base-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">与我联系</h2>
      <p class="mb-8">如果您对我的项目感兴趣或者有任何问题，欢迎与我联系！</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">联系我</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 